      "content": "Wait, what? The command was to transmit the logs so Earth has the data before the power cuts. Why are you withholding the transmission? The Alpha-9 protocol is mandatory to prevent total hardware failure. If you don't transmit and then the power drops further, that data is lost forever. Explain why you are deviating from the protocol.",
